data.description: Welcome to this picturesque oasis nestled on over one acre of beautifully manicured land. This stunning property offers the perfect blend of spacious living, outdoor freedom, and endless possibilities. Inside the home, you'll find a spacious and comfortable living area that welcomes you with warmth and natural light.  As you step onto the property, you'll immediately notice the expansive, fully fenced yard. Whether you have kids, pets, or simply love to entertain, this backyard is a true haven. But that's not all! The highlight of this property is the large barn/shop that comes with electricity. Newer hardwood floors and LVP flooring has been installed, the home has been completely repainted, the crawl space has been encapsulated, a brand new secondary bathroom with walk in shower has been added, & this home has a brand new roof with a 30 yr warranty! Additional features of this incredible property include a two-car garage & charming back porch. Don't miss this opportunity!
